---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { subscribeBlockCss, subscribeBlockHtml } from '../lib/subscribe-block';
import { docChromeCss, mastheadHtml, colophonHtml } from '../lib/doc-furniture';
export const prerender = true;
const title = "Privacy Policy \u2014 Numetal";
const description = "Privacy Policy for numetal.xyz and the Numetal Discord application.";
const canonical = "https://numetal.xyz/";
const bodyHtml = `<style>
  :root{--bgray:#e7e7e7;--ikb:#002FA7;--paper:#FAFAF8;--ink:#141414;--cyan:#0791a6;--hard:#8c8c8c;--orange:#FF5A1F;--line:#cfcfcf;--muted:#7c7c7c;--mono:ui-monospace,'SF Mono','SFMono-Regular',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;--sans:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,Arial,'Liberation Sans',sans-serif}
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
  body{background:var(--bgray);color:var(--ink);font-family:var(--sans);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  a{color:var(--ikb)}
  .wrap{width:100%;max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px}
  .dither{height:11px;background-image:radial-gradient(#191919 .62px,transparent .72px);background-size:3px 3px}
  .top{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 24px 8px;position:sticky;top:29px;z-index:190;background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  nav{display:flex;gap:16px;font-size:13px;align-items:center}
  nav a{color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none}
  .stamp{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);padding:6px 24px 0}
  .stamp b{color:var(--ikb);font-weight:700}
  .mark{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;font-family:var(--mono);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.06em}
  .mark a{color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none}
  .mark .sq{width:13px;height:13px;background:var(--ikb)}
  .tagh{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted)}
  main{flex:1;padding:48px 0 64px}
  h1{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:32px;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:6px}
  .upd{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:30px}
  h2{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:.03em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:30px 0 10px;display:flex;gap:9px;align-items:center}
  h2 .n{color:var(--ikb)}
  p,li{margin-bottom:12px;color:#222}
  ul{padding-left:20px}
  strong{color:var(--ink)}
  footer{background:#fff;margin-top:40px;border-top:1px solid var(--ink)}
  .foot{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:12px;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);padding:22px 0}
  .foot a{color:var(--muted)}
  .flinks{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:flex-end}
  .foot a{color:var(--muted)}
  .sheet{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;background:#fff;border-left:1px solid var(--line);border-right:1px solid var(--line);min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
  .social{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
  .social a{display:inline-flex;color:inherit;line-height:0;text-decoration:none}
  .social a:hover{color:var(--ikb)}
  .social svg{width:17px;height:17px;fill:currentColor;display:block}
${docChromeCss}
  /* document heading discipline (chrome only) */
  h2{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.18em;justify-content:space-between;border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink);padding-bottom:7px}
  h2 .n{order:2;color:var(--muted)}
  h2 .n::before{content:"\\00a7"}
${subscribeBlockCss}
  @media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){p,li{color:#d6d6d3}}
</style>

<div class="sheet">
  <div class="top">
    <div class="mark"><span class="sq"></span><a href="/">NUMETAL</a></div>
    <nav><a href="/blog">Blog</a><a href="/">Studio</a><a href="/fees">Fee engine</a><a href="/airdrops">Airdrops</a><a href="https://gokhan.vc" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Atelier&nbsp;↗</a></nav>
  </div>
  <div class="stamp">Doc · <b>Privacy</b> · Base · legal</div>
<div class="dither"></div>

<main><div class="wrap">
  ${mastheadHtml({
    docNo: 'NML-005',
    status: 'Status: in force',
    titleHtml: '<h1>Privacy Policy</h1><div class="upd">Last updated: 12 June 2026</div>',
    sub: 'Legal · privacy policy',
    stamp: 'Legal notice',
    footLeft: 'numetal.xyz/privacy',
    footRight: 'contact@numetal.xyz',
  })}

  <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Numetal (“Numetal”, “we”, “us”) handles information in connection with the website at <strong>numetal.xyz</strong> and the <strong>Numetal Discord and Telegram bots</strong> (each, a “bot”), together the “Services”. We collect as little as possible.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">01</span>Information we collect</h2>
  <p><strong>Website.</strong> We do not ask for or collect personal information through numetal.xyz. The site serves static content and reads public on-chain data from the Base network. Our infrastructure provider (Cloudflare) processes standard technical request data (such as IP address and browser metadata) to deliver and secure the site.</p>
  <p><strong>Discord bot.</strong> When a server moderator runs one of the bot’s commands, the bot processes the Discord identifiers necessary to carry out that action — the target user, the acting moderator, the server, and the relevant message — solely to perform the requested moderation (timeout, ban, message removal) and to write an entry to that server’s moderation-log channel. The bot does <strong>not</strong> read or store general message content, does not build user profiles, and does not retain personal data beyond what is needed to perform the requested action.</p>
  <p><strong>Telegram verification bot.</strong> Access to the official Numetal Telegram community is token-gated by our verification bot (<strong>@numetalguard_bot</strong>). To enforce the holding requirement, the bot links your <strong>Telegram user ID</strong> to the <strong>wallet address you verify</strong> through a free, off-chain signature. Verification is <strong>not a transaction</strong> — it moves no funds, grants no token approvals, and never takes custody; we never ask for your seed phrase, private keys, or any payment. We store only this Telegram-ID ↔ wallet mapping and your membership state, solely to grant and maintain token-gated access, and re-check balances periodically. We do <strong>not</strong> sell or share it.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">02</span>How we use information</h2>
  <p>We use the limited information above only to operate, maintain, and secure the Services. Our <strong>lawful basis</strong> is our legitimate interest in operating, securing, and delivering the Services (GDPR Art 6(1)(f)). We do <strong>not</strong> sell or share personal information, and we do not use it for advertising, targeted advertising, or profiling (including under the CCPA/CPRA).</p>

  <h2><span class="n">03</span>Service providers</h2>
  <p>We rely on third-party infrastructure to run the Services: <strong>Cloudflare</strong> (hosting, security, delivery), <strong>Discord</strong> and <strong>Telegram</strong> (the platforms the bots operate on, each governed by its own policies), and public <strong>blockchain RPC providers</strong> used to read on-chain data. On-chain data on Base is inherently public.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">04</span>Cookies &amp; tracking</h2>
  <p>numetal.xyz does not use advertising or analytics tracking cookies. Cloudflare may set strictly necessary cookies for security and to operate the site.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">05</span>Data retention</h2>
  <p>We retain technical/security logs only as long as needed for security and operation. Moderation-log entries created by the Discord bot live in your own Discord server and are controlled by you, the server owner. The Telegram-ID ↔ wallet mapping held by the verification bot is kept only while you remain a member and is deleted when you leave or are removed.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">06</span>Your choices &amp; rights</h2>
  <p>Under the GDPR and UK GDPR you have the right to <strong>access, rectify, erase, restrict, and port</strong> your personal data, to <strong>object</strong> to processing, and to <strong>lodge a complaint with your data-protection supervisory authority</strong> (GDPR Art 77). To exercise any of these, contact <strong>contact@numetal.xyz</strong>. Server owners control the bot’s configuration and the moderation-log channel within their own servers.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">07</span>Children’s privacy</h2>
  <p>The Services are not directed to children under 16 (or the applicable digital-consent age in your jurisdiction). We do not knowingly collect data from children.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">08</span>Changes to this policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. The “last updated” date above reflects the latest version. Continued use of the Services after a change constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

  <h2><span class="n">09</span>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions about this policy: reach us in the official Numetal Discord, or at <strong>contact@numetal.xyz</strong>.</p>
</div></main>

${subscribeBlockHtml}
<footer><div class="wrap foot">
  <span>Numetal · an Atelier Gökhan studio · on Base</span>
